<br>
She huffed and puffed and walked around waiting to see the scroll,but it wasnt long 'till she knew what the message was about.&quot;War!?&quot;She almost yelled out,it wasnt like anyone was really paying attention to her anyways,all she knew was she was brave and wanted to play too,not quite getting the entire concept of war.Young(7 yrs),and still learning things.<br>
<br>
She ran over and grabbed up her wooden sword which she had dropped earlier...&quot;Scooooooooby!!!!&quot;She yells out,and within moments her large Great-dane dog comes a running through the village toward Evelyn.Evelyn quickly holds her hands out.&quot;Woah Scooby,Woaaaah!&quot;She paniced,not wanting to get run over by the large dog that could easily crush her,and with her pleads,Scooby skids to a stop,but not fast enough,and Evelyn quickly jumps out of his way.<br>
<br>
Evelyn,out of breath from excitement,talks to Scooby.&quot;Okay Scooby,we gotsa go and help.&quot;And she climbs onto the back of the dog.&quot;Okay Scooby...&quot;She swallows nervously.&quot;....GO!&quot;And with that,Scooby takes off running.Evelyn clings to the the dogs scruff with her right hands and clutched her wooden sword with her left and lets out a childlike war cry,in which she had heared some of the amazons do before while sparing,but gives her lil warcry its own lil twist. &quot;Eeeeeeeeheheheya!!!!Scooby dooby dooooooooooooooooooo!&quot;<br>
Flopping about on the back of Scooby,she could be mistaken for a rag doll,but remarkably she is able to hold on for dear life as Scooby clumsily runs out of the village,following some of the amazons that too were heading to Scynthia. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.showMessage?topicID=19.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.emailToFriend?topicID=23.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.threadControl?topicID=23.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option